      <title>你忽略了的提醒</title>
      <link href="/2025/06/11/%E5%A4%AA%E6%99%9A%E4%BA%86/"/>
      <url>/2025/06/11/%E5%A4%AA%E6%99%9A%E4%BA%86/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="video-container">[up主专用，视频内嵌代码贴在这]</div><style>.video-container {    position: relative;    width: 100%;    padding-top: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio (height/width = 9/16 * 100%) */}.video-container iframe {    position: absolute;    top: 0;    left: 0;    width: 100%;    height: 100%;}</style><h1 id="你忽略了的提醒"><a href="#你忽略了的提醒" class="headerlink" title="你忽略了的提醒"></a>你忽略了的提醒</h1><h1 id="太晚了"><a href="#太晚了" class="headerlink" title="太晚了"></a>太晚了</h1><h2 id="今天我突然明白了，一个人最大的财富，就是出生在一个正常的地方，或者一个正常的家庭。"><a href="#今天我突然明白了，一个人最大的财富，就是出生在一个正常的地方，或者一个正常的家庭。" class="headerlink" title="今天我突然明白了，一个人最大的财富，就是出生在一个正常的地方，或者一个正常的家庭。"></a>今天我突然明白了，一个人最大的财富，就是出生在一个正常的地方，或者一个正常的家庭。</h2><h1 id="教育"><a href="#教育" class="headerlink" title="教育"></a>教育</h1><h2 id="教育是民族最伟大的生存原则，"><a href="#教育是民族最伟大的生存原则，" class="headerlink" title="教育是民族最伟大的生存原则，"></a>教育是民族最伟大的生存原则，</h2><h2 id="教育是一切社会把恶的数量减少，"><a href="#教育是一切社会把恶的数量减少，" class="headerlink" title="教育是一切社会把恶的数量减少，"></a>教育是一切社会把恶的数量减少，</h2><h2 id="教育是把善的数量增多的唯一的手段。"><a href="#教育是把善的数量增多的唯一的手段。" class="headerlink" title="教育是把善的数量增多的唯一的手段。"></a>教育是把善的数量增多的唯一的手段。</h2><h2 id="——奥诺雷·巴尔扎克"><a href="#——奥诺雷·巴尔扎克" class="headerlink" title="——奥诺雷·巴尔扎克"></a>——奥诺雷·巴尔扎克</h2><h1 id="回顾"><a href="#回顾" class="headerlink" title="回顾"></a>回顾</h1><h2 id="一个有创造力的人不会沉溺于过去的痛苦，他们会学会教训；而弱者则是整日沉浸在痛苦里，回顾以往的苦难来折磨自己。"><a href="#一个有创造力的人不会沉溺于过去的痛苦，他们会学会教训；而弱者则是整日沉浸在痛苦里，回顾以往的苦难来折磨自己。" class="headerlink" title="一个有创造力的人不会沉溺于过去的痛苦，他们会学会教训；而弱者则是整日沉浸在痛苦里，回顾以往的苦难来折磨自己。"></a>一个有创造力的人不会沉溺于过去的痛苦，他们会学会教训；而弱者则是整日沉浸在痛苦里，回顾以往的苦难来折磨自己。</h2><h2 id="——奥诺雷·巴尔扎克-​​​"><a href="#——奥诺雷·巴尔扎克-​​​" class="headerlink" title="——奥诺雷·巴尔扎克 ​​​"></a>——奥诺雷·巴尔扎克 ​​​</h2><h1 id="除非是为了从过去的错误中吸取有益的教训，并从来之不易的经验中获益，否则我们不应该回顾过去。–华盛顿"><a href="#除非是为了从过去的错误中吸取有益的教训，并从来之不易的经验中获益，否则我们不应该回顾过去。–华盛顿" class="headerlink" title="除非是为了从过去的错误中吸取有益的教训，并从来之不易的经验中获益，否则我们不应该回顾过去。–华盛顿"></a>除非是为了从过去的错误中吸取有益的教训，并从来之不易的经验中获益，否则我们不应该回顾过去。–华盛顿</h1><h1 id="Reminders-you-ignored"><a href="#Reminders-you-ignored" class="headerlink" title="Reminders you ignored"></a>Reminders you ignored</h1><h1 id="Too-late"><a href="#Too-late" class="headerlink" title="Too late"></a>Too late</h1><h2 id="Today-I-suddenly-understood-that-the-greatest-fortune-in-life-is-being-born-in-a-normal-place-or-into-a-normal-family"><a href="#Today-I-suddenly-understood-that-the-greatest-fortune-in-life-is-being-born-in-a-normal-place-or-into-a-normal-family" class="headerlink" title="Today, I suddenly understood that the greatest fortune in life is being born in a normal place or into a normal family."></a>Today, I suddenly understood that the greatest fortune in life is being born in a normal place or into a normal family.</h2><h1 id="Education"><a href="#Education" class="headerlink" title="Education"></a>Education</h1><h2 id="Education-is-the-greatest-living-principle-of-a-nation-and-it-can-also-reduce-the-number-of-crimes-in-society-It-is-the-only-way-to-increase-kindness-—-Balzac"><a href="#Education-is-the-greatest-living-principle-of-a-nation-and-it-can-also-reduce-the-number-of-crimes-in-society-It-is-the-only-way-to-increase-kindness-—-Balzac" class="headerlink" title="Education is the greatest living principle of a nation, and it can also reduce the number of crimes in society. It is the only way to increase kindness. — Balzac"></a>Education is the greatest living principle of a nation, and it can also reduce the number of crimes in society. It is the only way to increase kindness. — Balzac</h2><h1 id="Review"><a href="#Review" class="headerlink" title="Review"></a>Review</h1><h2 id="A-creative-person-cannot-be-consumed-by-past-pain-They-learn-from-their-failures-But-a-weak-person-wallows-in-pain-every-day-and-allows-it-to-torment-them-—-Balzac"><a href="#A-creative-person-cannot-be-consumed-by-past-pain-They-learn-from-their-failures-But-a-weak-person-wallows-in-pain-every-day-and-allows-it-to-torment-them-—-Balzac" class="headerlink" title="A creative person cannot be consumed by past pain. They learn from their failures. But a weak person wallows in pain every day and allows it to torment them. — Balzac"></a>A creative person cannot be consumed by past pain. They learn from their failures. But a weak person wallows in pain every day and allows it to torment them. — Balzac</h2><h2 id="We-shouldn’t-dwell-on-the-past—unless-we-seek-to-learn-from-our-failures-and-gain-valuable-lessons-from-them-—-Washington"><a href="#We-shouldn’t-dwell-on-the-past—unless-we-seek-to-learn-from-our-failures-and-gain-valuable-lessons-from-them-—-Washington" class="headerlink" title="We shouldn’t dwell on the past—unless we seek to learn from our failures and gain valuable lessons from them. — Washington"></a>We shouldn’t dwell on the past—unless we seek to learn from our failures and gain valuable lessons from them. — Washington</h2><p><img src="/./images/xican1.PNG" alt="xican1"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
