<h2 id="And-who-indeed-can-accomplish-the-truly-unforeseen"><a href="#And-who-indeed-can-accomplish-the-truly-unforeseen" class="headerlink" title="And who, indeed, can accomplish the truly unforeseen?"></a>And who, indeed, can accomplish the truly unforeseen?</h2><p><img src="/./images/holand.jpg" alt="holand"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
